Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike I would make a few bucks here and there but I never took it too seriously... May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike It wasn't all sunshine and roses either took some losses on the way, almost daily. Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike After 18 months of trading, I finally quit my 9-5 job as an engineer to become a trader. When quit, I was making $5k/m from my job and $10k/m from trading. Now, here's what process... learned in the the'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike 1. Trading is all about the fundamentals. 2. Discipline and patience is 80% of trading. 3.A A lot can happen wher on you craft for 2+ years. you focus continued...'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike The rest of my story is pretty boring. stayed consistent and continuously reinvested into my long-term investments and trading account for the next three years. That, and the help of starting my own business, is what helped me make my first $1,000,000.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @highstrike. May be an image of text that says 'HighStrike @highstrike Here on @highstrike, we make content daily to help you become a better and more responsible trader. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In high school, came across a social media marketing agency course. I realized could start that business because it didn't require a huge starting capital and could do it while was still at school. So I started my own agency.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. It was nothing special but it was decent money at the time and it solidified that could eventually pursue my business full time.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So in the final year of high school, had two options, either go to university or learn a trade. Photo shared by Entrepreneurship & Investing💲 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax I mostly got criticized for that but| didn't care and believed that made the right decision.
